<Link id="l01083" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1083" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">enum</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144">ProfVersion</a> &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01084" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1084"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Version 1 is the first version. In this version, the value of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01085" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1085"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// a key/value pair can only include profile data of a single function.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01086" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1086"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Due to this restriction, the number of block counters for a given</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01087" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1087"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// function is not recorded but derived from the length of the value.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01088" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1088" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144adf9c49729352ec5938aba7ee742f22eb"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144adf9c49729352ec5938aba7ee742f22eb">Version1</a> = 1,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01089" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1089"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The version 2 format supports recording profile data of multiple</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01090" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1090"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// functions which share the same key in one value field. To support this,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01091" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1091"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// the number block counters is recorded as an uint64&#95;t field right after the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01092" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1092"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// function structural hash.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01093" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1093" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144a9ee73a152159ed9b802491d123340ca1"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144a9ee73a152159ed9b802491d123340ca1">Version2</a> = 2,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01094" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1094"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Version 3 supports value profile data. The value profile data is expected</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01095" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1095"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// to follow the block counter profile data.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01096" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1096" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144a401026e6fd4e6d78f47d7d26553e9c08"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144a401026e6fd4e6d78f47d7d26553e9c08">Version3</a> = 3,</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01099" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1099" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144a4e22e7c95daa6961d2904589b2898fc6"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/indexedinstrprof/#afec2cd4aa77a3d0dfd1ea326732ef144a4e22e7c95daa6961d2904589b2898fc6">Version4</a> = 4,</span></CodeLine>
